column1: Smoque BBQ////We pretty much finished everything because we're gluttons and because it was so good it would have been a waste not to. And then they had to roll us out of there. But seriously
column2: I was full until lunch the next day. Next time
column3: I would probably not eat the rolls that come with the sandwiches. They are good enough
column4: but they take up valuable space in your stomach.
